So basically a part one, part two, without

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:03.180
actually naming it part one, part two, and

00:19:03.180 --> 00:19:06.860
essentially build a hook at the beginning of

00:19:06.860 --> 00:19:07.240
a video.

00:19:07.560 --> 00:19:09.480
And at the end of the video, we

00:19:09.480 --> 00:19:12.280
put a second, very strong hook, similar to

