00:19:19.920 --> 00:19:21.380
going to happen next or what's the next

00:19:21.380 --> 00:19:22.220
step, right?

00:19:22.460 --> 00:19:24.800
Basically a cliffhanger, like what the TV shows

00:19:24.800 --> 00:19:25.620
do all the time.

00:19:26.180 --> 00:19:28.240
So first of all, by doing that, by

00:19:28.240 --> 00:19:30.180
having this crazy hook there and then having

00:19:30.180 --> 00:19:32.220
a second hook, people watch all the way

00:19:32.220 --> 00:19:32.780
until the end.

00:19:32.860 --> 00:19:34.420
And then once they're at the end, they're

00:19:34.420 --> 00:19:36.060
like, oh, no, there's another thing.

00:19:36.220 --> 00:19:38.540
I want to now know the other thing.

00:19:38.700 --> 00:19:41.000
And then people are going to wait sometimes

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:42.400
for your next video to drop.

00:19:42.520 --> 00:19:43.740
You're going to get way more comments.

00:19:43.800 --> 00:19:46.680
And once the video drops, people come, you

00:19:46.680 --> 00:19:49.480
know, flooding to your content because they want

00:19:49.480 --> 00:19:51.960
to get their, I don't know what, satisfied,

00:19:52.240 --> 00:19:52.400
